text: Uģis Lasmanis (born 29 July 1967) is a Latvian rower. He competed at the 1992 Summer Olympics and the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1967 births Category:Living people Category:Latvian male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Latvia Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Rowers at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:People from Ventspils
